## üîë Why Security is Important (5 Core Reasons)

### 1Ô∏è‚É£ Protects Against External & Internal Threats

**Meaning:** Security system ‡¶¨‡¶æ‡¶á‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶è‡¶¨‡¶Ç ‡¶≠‡ßá‡¶§‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶¶‡ßÅ‡¶á ‡¶ß‡¶∞‡¶®‡ßá‡¶∞ threat ‡¶•‡ßá‡¶ï‡ßá protect ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá‡•§

* **External Threats:** hacker, malware, phishing, ransomware
* **Internal Threats:** employee mistake, insider attack, accidental data leak

**Example:**
Firewall + Access Control ‡¶•‡¶æ‡¶ï‡¶≤‡ßá:

* Outside hacker ‡¶¢‡ßÅ‡¶ï‡¶§‡ßá ‡¶™‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßá ‡¶®‡¶æ
* Inside employee ‡¶∏‡¶¨ data access ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡¶§‡ßá ‡¶™‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßá ‡¶®‡¶æ

---

### 2Ô∏è‚É£ Meets Regulatory Compliance

**Meaning:** Organization ‡¶Ü‡¶á‡¶® ‡¶ì government security rules follow ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá‡•§

**Examples:**

* Data protection law
* Banking regulations
* Health data rules

**Example:**
Bank ‡¶Ø‡¶¶‡¶ø customer data encrypt ‡¶®‡¶æ ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá ‚Üí ‚ùå Law violation ‚Üí üí∏ Fine
Security ‡¶•‡¶æ‡¶ï‡¶≤‡ßá ‚Üí ‚úÖ Compliance ‚Üí No legal issue

---

### 3Ô∏è‚É£ Maintains & Improves Business Productivity

**Meaning:** Secure system ‡¶•‡¶æ‡¶ï‡¶≤‡ßá business downtime ‡¶π‡ßü ‡¶®‡¶æ‡•§

**Example:**
