## üîê CIA Triad (Core Security Principle)

### 1Ô∏è‚É£ Confidentiality

Only authorized users data access ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡¶§‡ßá ‡¶™‡¶æ‡¶∞‡¶¨‡ßá
**Examples:** Encryption, Access control

### 2Ô∏è‚É£ Integrity

Data accurate ‡¶ì unchanged ‡¶•‡¶æ‡¶ï‡¶¨‡ßá
**Examples:** Hashing, Checksums

### 3Ô∏è‚É£ Availability

Authorized users ‡¶∏‡¶Æ‡ßü‡¶Æ‡¶§‡ßã data access ‡¶™‡¶æ‡¶¨‡ßá
**Examples:** Backup, Redundancy

> **CIA = Foundation of Cybersecurity**

