## üÜî Protecting Personally Identifiable Information (PII)

### üîπ PII (Personally Identifiable Information)

‡¶Ø‡ßá data ‡¶¶‡¶ø‡ßü‡ßá ‡¶è‡¶ï‡¶ú‡¶® ‡¶Æ‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßÅ‡¶∑‡¶ï‡ßá identify ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡¶æ ‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡ßü:

