## CISSP Security Domains Mapping

### üß† What We Covered ‚Äî CISSP 8 Domain ‡¶¶‡¶ø‡ßü‡ßá ‡¶∏‡¶π‡¶ú ‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶ñ‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ
**Covered Topics:**  
