### üß© CISSP 8 Domain ‡¶Æ‡¶®‡ßá ‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶∞ SUPER EASY Trick
**Sentence to remember:**  
> ‚ÄúRisky Assets Are Carefully Identified, Assessed, Operated, and Developed Securely‚Äù

**Mapping:**

| Shortcut       | CISSP Domain                     |
|----------------|---------------------------------|
| Risky          | Security & Risk Management       |
| Assets         | Asset Security                   |
| Are Carefully  | Security Architecture & Engineering |
| Identified     | Communication & Network Security |
| Identified     | Identity & Access Management     |
| Assessed       | Security Assessment & Testing    |
| Operated       | Security Operations              |
| Developed Securely | Software Development Security  |

---

